   219→## Output and signalling failure
   220→
   221→While it's nice to print word counts to the terminal when a book is built, it
   222→might also be a good idea to output them to a file somewhere. `mdbook` tells a
   223→backend where it should place any generated output via the `destination` field
   224→in [`RenderContext`].
   225→
      →…
