     3→In addition to providing runnable code playgrounds, mdBook optionally allows them
     4→to be editable. In order to enable editable code blocks, the following needs to
     5→be added to the ***book.toml***:
     6→
     7→```toml
     8→[output.html.playground]
     9→editable = true
