    82→## Improve default theme
    83→
    84→If you think the default theme doesn't look quite right for a specific language,
    85→or could be improved, feel free to [submit a new
    86→issue](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/issues) explaining what you
    87→have in mind and I will take a look at it.
    88→
    89→You could also create a pull-request with the proposed improvements.
